{"application": "software-mentions", "version": "0.8.0", "date": "2024-10-07T12:44+0000", "md5": "4D2B0431E2861DC8FE293D935C332DE2", "mentions": [{"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "FASST", "normalizedForm": "FASST", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 5}, "context": "FASST is based on local Gaussian modeling in the time-frequency domain. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.10987567901611328}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 6.580352783203125e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9866846203804016}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.42883068323135376}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014)", "normalizedForm": "Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014", "refKey": 29}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "FASST", "normalizedForm": "FASST", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 5}, "context": "FASST can partially recover from such bad initialization thanks to the information provided by the pretrained template spectra, but not always.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 3.1828880310058594e-05}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 9.179115295410156e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9866846203804016}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.42883068323135376}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014)", "normalizedForm": "Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014", "refKey": 29}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DIRHA", "normalizedForm": "DIRHA", "offsetStart": 4, "offsetEnd": 9}, "context": "The DIRHA Simulated corpus (Cristoforetti et al., 2014) was generated in a similar way, with more microphones across several rooms and simulated noise backgrounds obtained by summing individually recorded noises. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9859506487846375}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 9.298324584960938e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9859506487846375}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.3589859008789062e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.2755393981933594e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "DIRHA", "normalizedForm": "DIRHA", "offsetStart": 4, "offsetEnd": 9}, "context": "The DIRHA-English corpus (Ravanelli et al., 2015) and the Sweet-Home corpus (Vacher et al., 2014) relax this constraint, but are not publicly available 2 .", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.461948037147522}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.3589859008789062e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.2755393981933594e-05}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9859506487846375}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.3589859008789062e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.2755393981933594e-05}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "FASST toolbox", "normalizedForm": "FASST toolbox", "offsetStart": 36, "offsetEnd": 49}, "context": "This is done by a first call to the FASST toolbox, where the template spectra are initialized by vector quantization of the input magnitude spectrogram. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.8042336106300354}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00011777877807617188}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.8042336106300354}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00011777877807617188}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "FASST", "normalizedForm": "FASST", "offsetStart": 37, "offsetEnd": 42}, "context": "This is achieved by a second call to FASST, where the spatial covariance matrices are initialized via a rank-1 model computed from the DOA of the noise source. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.4641876816749573}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.777576446533203e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9866846203804016}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.42883068323135376}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014)", "normalizedForm": "Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014", "refKey": 29}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Kaldi", "normalizedForm": "Kaldi", "offsetStart": 39, "offsetEnd": 64}, "context": "The ASR baseline was implemented using Kaldi (Povey et al., 2011).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9962583780288696}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00012564659118652344}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9962583780288696}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00012564659118652344}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "FASST", "normalizedForm": "FASST", "offsetStart": 65, "offsetEnd": 70}, "context": "Finally, actual source separation is performed by a last call to FASST, using the previously trained models and the speaker DOA to initialize its spatial covariance matrix. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.969119131565094}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.3828277587890625e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9866846203804016}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.42883068323135376}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014)", "normalizedForm": "Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014", "refKey": 29}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "environment", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Matlab", "normalizedForm": "Matlab", "offsetStart": 144, "offsetEnd": 150}, "context": "We made this implementation freely available, together with 7 other angular spectrum-based localization techniques (Blandin et al., 2012), in a Matlab toolbox named Multichannel BSS Locate10 .", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0023537278175354004}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9110889434814453}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.0018027424812316895}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0023537278175354004}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9110889434814453}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.0018027424812316895}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "FASST", "normalizedForm": "FASST", "offsetStart": 145, "offsetEnd": 150}, "context": "We replicated the strategy deployed by Ozerov and Vincent (2011) and adapted it to perform source separation on the voiceHome-2 corpus using the FASST toolbox (Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014) 12 . ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9866846203804016}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.42883068323135376}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9866846203804016}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.42883068323135376}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014)", "normalizedForm": "Sala\u00fcn et al., 2014", "refKey": 29, "offsetStart": 30080, "offsetEnd": 30101}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Locate", "normalizedForm": "Locate", "offsetStart": 182, "offsetEnd": 190}, "context": "We made this implementation freely available, together with 7 other angular spectrum-based localization techniques (Blandin et al., 2012), in a Matlab toolbox named Multichannel BSS Locate10 .", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0023537278175354004}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9110889434814453}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.0018027424812316895}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0023537278175354004}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9110889434814453}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.0018027424812316895}}}], "references": [{"refKey": 29, "tei": "<biblStruct xml:id=\"b29\">\n\t<monogr>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">Y</forename><surname>Sala\u00fcn</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">E</forename><surname>Vincent</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">N</forename><surname>Bertin</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">N</forename><surname>Souvira\u00e0-Labastie</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">X</forename><surname>Jaureguiberry</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">D</forename><forename type=\"middle\">T</forename><surname>Tran</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><forename type=\"first\">F</forename><surname>Bimbot</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<title level=\"m\">The Flexible Audio Source Separation Toolbox Version 2</title>\n\t\t<imprint>\n\t\t\t<publisher>ICASSP Show &am